  "local_port": 44578,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How is Iphone 6s better than 6?",
  "response": "The iPhone 6s, introduced by Apple in September 2015, brought several improvements and new features over its predecessor, the iPhone 6. Here are some key areas where the iPhone 6s is considered better than the iPhone 6:\n\n1. **Performance**: \n   - The iPhone 6s is powered by the A9 chip with 64-bit architecture, which is significantly faster and more efficient than the A8 chip in the iPhone 6. This results in better overall performance and responsiveness.\n\n2. **Camera Improvements**:\n   - The rear camera was upgraded from 8 megapixels in the iPhone 6 to 12 megapixels in the iPhone 6s, allowing for higher resolution photos and 4K video recording.\n   - The front camera received an upgrade as well, increasing from 1.2 megapixels to 5 megapixels, improving selfie quality and FaceTime video calls.\n\n3. **3D Touch**:\n   - The iPhone 6s introduced 3D Touch technology, which allows the screen to detect pressure sensitivity, enabling new ways to interact with the device, such as \"Peek and Pop\" previews and Quick Actions.\n\n4. **Build Quality**:\n   - The iPhone 6s uses 7000 series aluminum, which is stronger and more durable than the aluminum used in the iPhone 6, addressing some concerns about bending.\n\n5. **Live Photos**:\n   - This feature, introduced with the iPhone 6s, captures a short video clip along with a still photo, allowing users to see moments before and after a picture is taken.\n\n6. **Improved Touch ID**:\n   - The second-generation Touch ID in the iPhone 6s is faster and more accurate compared to the first-generation Touch ID in the iPhone 6.\n\n7. **Improved Connectivity**:\n   - The iPhone 6s supports faster LTE speeds and more LTE bands for better global roaming capability. It also has faster Wi-Fi speeds with Wi-Fi 802.11ac.\n\n8. **Increased RAM**:\n   - The iPhone 6s has 2GB of RAM compared to 1GB in the iPhone 6, resulting in better multitasking performance.\n\nWhile both phones share a similar design, these improvements in the iPhone 6s contribute to a substantially enhanced user experience compared to the iPhone 6.",
